page.title: 16TYPICAL DAY & WEEKEND
page.content: {Typical schoolday My mother wakes me at 7 I get up,wash and put in my contact lenses before dressing. I usually have a poached egg and a cup of tea for breakfast. I prepare my{school books,}it takes me 5 minutes to cycle to Haybridge. School starts at 8:55. My day involves subjects such as Maths., English, French,Chemistry,Needlework and Woodwork.At 12 I buy my lunch from the school canteen before lessons restart at 1:15. School ends at 3:45. In the{evening,}I watch T.V.,play on my computer,or visit friends.I usually go to bed at 11. {Typical weekend { }On Saturday, I get up at 8:45 to do my paper round. I often spend my morning around Halesowen, and in the evening may go to Silver Blades (ice rink). On Sunday I lie in bed.
